Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,影片开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,大概又不行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:00:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊什么征选异世界用的男优
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.51,0:01:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那个超瞎扯的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,反正十之八九没我们的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,今天谢谢你们来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.46,0:01:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为想当AV男优
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,每天锻炼体格和固定打枪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哪边啊这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真是无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有人耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,说话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.44,0:05:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,魔王部下对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,等等这是怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,一定不是好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,宰了他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,拿来做武器好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大家聊天说的什么异世界设定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这是所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,异世界招唤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,过来我就丢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:07:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不准动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,禁止暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,暴力反对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你们唱戏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,经验值有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但东西也没啥值钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,算啦走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,干么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.39,0:11:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,请问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,传说中的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,大坏蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有本事都不见得能抓到他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会有兴趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那我你找点伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.41,0:14:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,被史莱姆攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,失去意识的战士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,看样子是没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这边收获也很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真赞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有个战士妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.45,0:15:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,被史莱姆搞昏倒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,先看看有没有东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没有东西的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,要好好搜查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.46,0:20:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.38,0:21:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉爽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这样爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.45,0:22:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,都湿了呢
