Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.46,0:31:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,插入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.48,0:31:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真赞
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.40,0:37:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.49,0:38:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真赞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.49,0:42:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.47,0:42:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.45,0:43:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
