Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.39,0:46:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这边是怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.46,0:46:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,到底是哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.40,0:46:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.66,0:46:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.41,0:47:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.38,0:48:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,走开
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.45,0:48:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,走开?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.39,0:48:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,听的懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.46,0:48:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.40,0:48:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.47,0:48:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.41,0:48:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.51,0:49:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.40,0:49:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,啊怎么是你
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.47,0:49:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啊起混的汁男二!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.42,0:49:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你也来到这了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.49,0:49:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.44,0:50:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.51,0:50:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.39,0:50:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我稍微研究了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.46,0:50:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这边的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.40,0:50:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上就真的是rpg
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.47,0:50:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.41,0:50:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,升级比较特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.48,0:50:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不是太难
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.42,0:50:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.49,0:51:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要需要锻炼
