Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.50,1:37:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.44,1:37:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.51,1:38:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啦
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.45,1:38:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你要更加努力升级
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.45,1:39:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这边是靠腕力的世界
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.39,1:39:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.46,1:39:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,锻炼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.47,1:39:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.41,1:39:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.48,1:39:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,碰面好高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.42,1:39:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.49,1:39:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.43,1:39:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,应该这样说吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:01.50,1:40:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,而且呢
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.44,1:40:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这边是
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.51,1:40:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真的异世界
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.45,1:40:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们更应该
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.52,1:40:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.46,1:40:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.39,1:40:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,说的好
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.43,1:41:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.51,1:41:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.44,1:41:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对了请问
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.52,1:41:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.40,1:41:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我是壹条
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.41,1:41:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,传说中最强的战士吗
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.49,1:42:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,预备
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.43,1:42:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.50,1:42:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,壹条胜利
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.51,1:42:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.45,1:42:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,再来来
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.40,1:42:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我说大姐
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.47,1:42:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你太强了啦
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.41,1:43:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.48,1:43:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要变强的话
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.42,1:43:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.49,1:43:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我们吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.46,1:43:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.40,1:43:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你也愿意帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,1:44:06.41,1:44:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.43,1:44:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.51,1:44:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:45:01.40,1:45:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.42,1:45:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.44,1:45:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,1:45:51.45,1:45:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,1:46:21.48,1:46:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.45,1:46:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很好喔
Dialogue: 0,1:47:16.47,1:47:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.42,1:47:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,1:48:06.52,1:48:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒
Dialogue: 0,1:48:26.40,1:48:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.42,1:48:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吧
Dialogue: 0,1:48:56.43,1:48:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,起变强吧
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.50,1:49:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.51,1:49:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.51,1:53:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.46,2:00:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,插入吧
Dialogue: 0,2:10:41.47,2:10:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,2:11:21.51,2:11:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,2:15:56.45,2:15:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,2:16:01.39,2:16:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,起来吧
Dialogue: 0,2:16:16.47,2:16:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我
Dialogue: 0,2:16:26.48,2:16:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,2:16:31.42,2:16:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,2:16:36.49,2:16:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,再来吧
Dialogue: 0,2:18:16.46,2:18:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,2:18:21.40,2:18:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,2:18:26.47,2:18:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,2:18:31.41,2:18:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不是应该
Dialogue: 0,2:18:36.48,2:18:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,会升级吗
Dialogue: 0,2:18:46.49,2:18:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,照着升级了
Dialogue: 0,2:19:51.49,2:19:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这哪边啊
Dialogue: 0,2:20:06.44,2:20:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么被绑起来了
Dialogue: 0,2:20:21.52,2:20:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,2:20:26.46,2:20:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱动喔
Dialogue: 0,2:20:41.40,2:20:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,2:20:46.48,2:20:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,2:20:51.41,2:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,别乱动
Dialogue: 0,2:20:56.49,2:20:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我很困扰
Dialogue: 0,2:21:36.39,2:21:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你干么啊
Dialogue: 0,2:36:36.49,2:36:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样呢主人
Dialogue: 0,2:38:11.52,2:38:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啊不行了
Dialogue: 0,2:40:26.46,2:40:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,主人请听话过来
Dialogue: 0,2:40:56.49,2:40:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,干么
Dialogue: 0,2:41:01.42,2:41:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,插入吗
Dialogue: 0,2:41:06.50,2:41:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我最会了
Dialogue: 0,2:43:06.48,2:43:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,2:43:46.39,2:43:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,再来啊
Dialogue: 0,2:43:51.46,2:43:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,还要继续吗
Dialogue: 0,2:44:11.48,2:44:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧主人
Dialogue: 0,2:49:16.45,2:49:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们继续吧主人
Dialogue: 0,2:49:41.41,2:49:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,定期吁购的杂志应该送到了吧¨
Dialogue: 0,2:49:51.42,2:49:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,唉呀没收的铁梯会锈掉吧
Dialogue: 0,2:51:01.49,2:51:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,只好继续前进到回家为止啦
Dialogue: 0,2:51:46.47,2:51:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,(影片结束)
